description:
Join us for Season two as we continue our epic journey and show you how God led his people after the Reformation. We feature the legacies of many unknown pioneers of the Seventh Day Adventist Church. We travel to the new frontiers as the light of the gospel increased and went around whole world, visiting America, Europe, Australia and New Zealand. 

#KnowYourHistory #KnowYourMission #Lineage #LineageJourney 

www.lineagejourney.com
